2025-09-18AAFC, TBFederal Real Property and Federal Immovables ActAdministration of Federal Real Property ** Agreement **Order authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into an agreement with His Majesty, in right of the Province of Alberta, for the administration and control of the federal real property located at 5403, 1st Avenue South, Lethbridge, Alberta for a term of 10 years, with an option to extend for 10 years.Registration: UNR/
act: Federal Real Property and Federal Immovables Act
subject: Administration of Federal Real Property ** Agreement **
precis: Order authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into an agreement with His Majesty, in right of the Province of Alberta, for the administration and control of the federal real property located at 5403, 1st Avenue South, Lethbridge, Alberta for a term of 10 years, with an option to extend for 10 years.
